{"lemma":"قُرْصٌ","slug":"قُرْصٌ","root":"ق.ر.ص","root_slug":"ق-ر-ص","root_link":"/words/roots/ق-ر-ص","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":3,"pos_tags":["noun","verb"],"has_etymology":true,"sense_count":7},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n35490","n42600"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D9%82%D9%8F%D8%B1%D9%92%D8%B5%D9%8C"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to pinch"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to pinch; to clean with fingers (by pinching)","examples":[{"text":"قَرَصَ الثَّوْبَ بِالْمَاءِ","english":"He cleaned the cloth with the water (by pinching it)."}]},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to bite, to sting"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"pinch, pinching"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"biting, stinging"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"disk (in most meanings, including technology-related)"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"tablet, pill"}]},"etymology":{"source":"wiktextract","text":"From Proto-Semitic *ḳaraṣ-, from the root ق ر ص (q r ṣ).\n\nDerived from the verbal noun of قَرَصَ (qaraṣa), from the root ق ر ص (q r ṣ).\n\nFrom the root ق ر ص (q r ṣ). There is no evidence that it might be borrowed."},"ipa":["/qa.ra.sˤa/","/qarsˤ/","/qursˤ/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n35490","headword_ar":"قُرْصٌ","root":"qrS","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"quroSapN","text_ar":"قُرْصَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A round cake"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, * TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of bread;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K, TA;) syn."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xubozapN","text_ar":"خُبْزَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ragiyfN","text_ar":"رَغِيفٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (TA:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"such as is very small:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA:) [or, accord. to present usage,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"small, but thick:"},{"kind":"text","text":"] the former word is the more common: (TA:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"round"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"piece of dough:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, A: *) [and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"any similar thing, small, and of a round, flattened form:"},{"kind":"text","text":"] pl., (of the former, S, Msb,)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aqoraASN","text_ar":"اَقْرَاصٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[a pl. of pauc.] and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qiraSapN","text_ar":"قِرَصَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, M, Msb, K) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qiraASN","text_ar":"قِرَاصٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (M, TA,) [both pls. of mult.;] and (of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"quroSapN","text_ar":"قُرْصَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", S, TA,)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"quraSN","text_ar":"قُرَصٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (S, K;) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aqoriSapN","text_ar":"اَقْرِصَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[is a pl. of pauc. of either]. (K, art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bt","text_ar":"بت"},{"kind":"text","text":".) ―         -b2-  Hence, as being likened to the thing above mentioned, (M,)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlquroSu","text_ar":"القُرْصُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (M, TA,) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"quroSu Al$~amosi","text_ar":"قُرْصُ الشَّمْسِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, A, TA,) or ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlquroSapu","text_ar":"القُرْصَةُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The disk"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Eayon","text_ar":"عَيْن"},{"kind":"text","text":")"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of the sun:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, M, K, TA:) and sometimes"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the sun,"},{"kind":"text","text":"as a common, or general, term: (M:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the disk"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Eyn","text_ar":"عين"},{"kind":"text","text":")"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of the sun when it is setting:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA:) you say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gaAba quroSu Al$~amosi","text_ar":"غَابَ قُرْصُ الشَّمْسِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the disk of the sun set,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"disappeared"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: (A, TA:) or the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Eyn","text_ar":"عين"},{"kind":"text","text":"of the sun is called ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"quroSap","text_ar":"قُرْصَة","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", with"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"p","text_ar":"ة"},{"kind":"text","text":", at the setting. (Lth, TA.) ―         -b3-  See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"muqar~aSN","text_ar":"مُقَرَّصٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". ―         -b4-  ["},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"quroSu $ahodK","text_ar":"قُرْصُ شَهْدٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EasalK","text_ar":"عَسَلٍ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A honey-comb:"},{"kind":"text","text":"or the same, and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$ahodK","text_ar":"شَهْدٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"quroSapu","text_ar":"قُرْصَةُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EasalK","text_ar":"عَسَلٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a portion of a honey-comb:"},{"kind":"text","text":"pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qiraSap","text_ar":"قِرَصَة"},{"kind":"text","text":".]"}],"source_refs":["K","TA","S","M","Msb","A"]},{"entry_id":"n42600","headword_ar":"قُرْصٌ","root":"qrS","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A round convex ornament"},{"kind":"text","text":"worn on the crown of the tarboosh. (See Modern Egypt. Appendix A.)"}],"source_refs":[]}]},"classical_definitions":null}